<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-6 left outline">
    <%= render partial: "shared/adventure_title" %>
    <p>The curious cat <br />
       Falling down down down the well <br />
       Cuddy needs your help!
    </p>
<p>
Oh No! Cuddy ran ahead of Mr. Chips and fell down a well. It is very dark inside the well. Cuddy finds a tin can with a string leading to the top of the well. He needs your help to place the call (he thinks the phone works). Let’s try to call Cuddy’s agent, PrettyP.
</p>
<p>On the right, in the terminal window try placing a call to PrettyP.</p>

<p>Type in this code:</p>
<code class="code-example">$Net::HTTP.get_response(URI('http://prettyp.herokuapp.com'))</code>
<p>
( Psst: Don’t type in the $ sign. That just means type it in to the section on the right. )</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6 pull-right outline">
      <div class="left replbox">
      <%= form_tag request.path, method: :put do %>
        <%= text_field_tag :ripl_input,"", class: "inputform" %>
        <%= submit_tag "submit" %>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    <div class="pull-left instructions">
      <p>enter / return - Submit code</p>
      <p>next - Move to the next lesson</p>
      <p>back - Return to previous lesson</p>
    </div> 
    <div class="smallpics pull-left">
      <%= image_tag("well-sm.jpg") %>
    </div>
 </div>
</div>
</div>
